data.title: Flowmaster Force II Cat-back Exhaust System - 2015-2016 Ford F-150 3.5L Ecoboost - 817727
data.description:
Flowmaster Part #817727

Test Vehicle: 2015 Ford F-150 3.5L Ecoboost

Application:
2015-2016 Ford F-150 with 2.7L/3.5L EcoBoost, 3.5L TiVCT or 5.0L Engine, All Except Std Cab/Short Bed.

Features:
Flowmaster's Force II Cat-back exhaust system for the 2015-2016 Ford F-150 is perfect for the person looking for a mild exterior sound level while maintaining a moderate interior sound with all of the performance benefits that you would expect from Flowmaster. This bolt on 409S stainless steel system for the 2.7L, 3.5L EcoBoost V6, 3.5L TiVCT V6 and 5.0L V8 engines features 3.00in mandrel bent tubing that flows into a 70 Series muffler and then exits into a 3.00in tailpipe. The system is finished off with a 4.00in double walled stainless steel tip. This system fits all cab and bed configurations except Standard Cab/Short Bed models. The exhaust system is manufactured in the USA and is covered by Flowmaster's Lifetime Limited Warranty. Designed for an easy fit, this system includes all necessary parts and hardware for installation.

data.title: Flowmaster Outlaw Cat-back Exhaust System - 2015-2016 Ford F150 - 2.7L Ecoboost - 817726
data.description:
Flowmaster Part #817726

Test Vehicle: 2015 Ford F-150 2.7L Ecoboost

Application:
Fits 2015-2016 Ford F-150 with 2.7L/3.5L Ecoboost, 3.5L TiVCT V6 or 5.0L V8 Engine, All Except Std Cab/Short Bed.

Features:
Flowmaster's Outlaw Cat-back exhaust system for the 2015-2016 Ford F-150 is perfect for the person looking for a very deep and aggressive sound level outside and inside the truck with all of the performance benefits that you would expect from Flowmaster. This exhaust is not for the faint of heart! This bolt-on DOR/DOS (Dual Out Rear, Dual Out Side) emissions-legal system for trucks with the 2.7L/3.5L Ecoboost, 3.5L TiVCT and 5.0L V8 engines features a Super 10 Series muffler and dual mandrel bent 3.00" tailpipes for maximum performance. The system is built out of 409S stainless steel and has 4.00" Black Stainless Steel Flowmaster Embossed tips. The exhaust system is manufactured in the USA and is covered by Flowmaster's Lifetime Limited Warranty. Designed for an easy fit, this system includes all necessary parts and hardware for installation.
